<subSubSection id="C37416F0F45AFFA7FF656B9E581FFC83" pageId="5" pageNumber="132" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BD1457BF45AFFA7FF656B9E581FFC83" blockId="5.[136,1452,158,797]" pageId="5" pageNumber="132">
<emphasis id="B91A9969F45AFFA7FF656B9E5A1FFD4B" bold="true" box="[189,328,698,724]" pageId="5" pageNumber="132">Comments:</emphasis>
— 
<taxonomicName id="4C6E3EF8F45AFFA7FEBC6B9E596BFD4B" authorityName="Aime &amp; McTaggart" authorityYear="2020" baseAuthorityName="Racib." box="[356,572,698,724]" class="Pucciniomycetes" family="Crossopsoraceae" genus="Neoolivea" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Fungi" order="Pucciniales" pageId="5" pageNumber="132" phylum="Basidiomycota" rank="species" species="tectonae">
<emphasis id="B91A9969F45AFFA7FEBC6B9E596BFD4B" box="[356,572,698,724]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="132">Neoolivea tectonae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is reported for the first time for 
<collectingCountry id="F37905EBF45AFFA7FC716B9E58BBFD4B" box="[937,1004,698,724]" name="Benin" pageId="5" pageNumber="132">Benin</collectingCountry>
and for the second time for Africa. The morphological characteristics observed for specimens from 
<collectingCountry id="F37905EBF45AFFA7FCEE6BFA582EFD67" box="[822,889,734,760]" name="Benin" pageId="5" pageNumber="132">Benin</collectingCountry>
